'''双溪哥本大桥'''（{{lang-ms|'''Jambatan Sungai Kebun'''}}、[[爪夷文|爪夷文]]：'''جمبتن سوڠاي کبون'''），正式名称为'''本基兰·阿纳克·哈嘉·莎莉哈苏丹后大桥'''（{{lang-ms|'''Jambatan Raja Isteri Pengiran Anak Hajah Saleha'''}}），以现任[[文莱苏丹|文莱苏丹]][[哈桑纳尔·博尔基亚|哈桑纳尔·博尔基亚]]的妻子、{{le|莎莉哈苏丹后|Queen Saleha of Brunei}}的名字命名，是[[文莱达鲁萨兰国|文莱达鲁萨兰国]]的一座单塔[[混凝土|混凝土]][[斜拉桥|斜拉桥]]，跨越[[文莱河|文莱河]]，连接[[斯里巴加湾市|斯里巴加湾市]]与[[文莱摩拉县|文莱摩拉县]]的{{le|双溪哥本|Sungai Kebun, Brunei-Muara}}，是文莱的第一座斜拉桥<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://borneobulletin.com.bn/raja-isteri-pengiran-anak-hajah-saleha-bridge-inaugurated/|title=Raja Isteri Pengiran Anak Hajah Saleha Bridge inaugurated|date=2017-10-15|work=Borneo Bulletin Online|language=en|access-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015203654/https://borneobulletin.com.bn/raja-isteri-pengiran-anak-hajah-saleha-bridge-inaugurated/|archive-date=2017-10-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。于2017年10月14日正式通车<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://thescoop.co/2017/10/14/bruneis-landmark-bridge-opens-heralds-new-era-development/|title=Brunei's landmark bridge opens, heralds new era of development|date=2017-10-14|work=The Scoop|language=en|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2017-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214133301/https://thescoop.co/2017/10/14/bruneis-landmark-bridge-opens-heralds-new-era-development/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://borneobulletin.com.bn/temburong-bridge-completed-2019-end/|title=Temburong Bridge to be completed by 2019 end|date=2017-03-15|work=Borneo Bulletin Online|language=en|access-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619065107/http://borneobulletin.com.bn/temburong-bridge-completed-2019-end/|archive-date=2017-06-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 设计 ==
大桥全长{{convert|622|m|0}}，主跨{{convert|300|m|0}}<ref name=":2">{{cite news|url=https://www.daelim.co.kr/eng/daelim/pr/NewsView.do?idx=11314|title=Daelim Holds Groundbreaking Ceremony for Brunei Sungai Kebun Bridge|date=2014-01-16|publisher=Daelim|language=en|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202959/http://www.daelim.co.kr/eng/daelim/pr/NewsView.do?idx=11314|dead-url=no}}</ref>，单主塔的塔高为157米<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.daelim.co.kr/eng/daelim/pr/NewsView.do?cd_mnu=EU035&idx=16393|title=Daelim Completes Islamic Dome Installation at the top of Sungai Brunei Bridge Tower|publisher=Daelim|language=en|date=2016-08-20|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202512/http://www.daelim.co.kr/eng/daelim/pr/NewsView.do?cd_mnu=EU035&idx=16393|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1" />，塔顶安装了[[伊斯兰|伊斯兰]][[圆顶|圆顶]]作为塔冠，[[直径|直径]]8.7米，重9.5[[公吨|公吨]]<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":1" />，桥塔自此成为文莱的最高[[建筑物|建筑物]]<ref name=":3" />。大桥是单塔跨径世界第二长的混凝土斜拉桥<ref>{{cite web|url=http://silkroad.news.cn/2017/1016/64751.shtml|title=文莱首座斜拉桥正式竣工通车|date=2017-10-16|work=新华社|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2018-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108062850/http://silkroad.news.cn/2017/1016/64751.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。桥面设置双向四[[车道|车道]][[公路|公路]]，连接大桥两端的[[互通立交|互通立交]]，同时桥上设有[[人行道|人行道]]<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|url=https://thescoop.co/2017/10/03/motorists-eager-new-sungai-kebun-bridge/|title=Motorists eager to drive across new Sungai Kebun bridge|date=2017-10-03|work=The Scoop|language=en|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2017-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205081059/https://thescoop.co/2017/10/03/motorists-eager-new-sungai-kebun-bridge/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

塔座建在一座[[新月|新月]]形小岛上，其形状类似潘吉潘吉（Panji-Panji）或[[文莱国徽|文莱国徽]]，岛上建有一座小楼，为一所[[美术馆|美术馆]]。

