== 历史 ==
作为“第十个国家发展计划”的一部分，文莱发展部于2013年6月成功启动了大桥项目的建设，开工仪式于2014年1月16日举行，由[[穆赫塔迪·比拉|穆赫塔迪·比拉王储]]主持<ref name=":2" />。大桥由[[韩国|韩国]]{{le|大林工业|Daelim}}和文莱建丰（Swee）组成的联合体承建，总造价1.389亿[[汶莱元|汶莱元]]（约合1.03亿[[美元|美元]]）<ref name="daelim">{{Cite web|url=http://m.koreaittimes.com/story/28591/daelim-industrial-build-sungai-brunei-bridge-brunei|title=Daelim Industrial to Build Sungai Brunei Bridge in Brunei|website=Korea IT Times|language=en|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202908/http://m.koreaittimes.com/story/28591/daelim-industrial-build-sungai-brunei-bridge-brunei|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="swee">{{Cite news|url=http://www.the-businessreport.com/article/swee-bridges-brunei-together/|title=Swee Sdn Bhd - Brunei - Construction Bridge - Bobby Chua|work=The Business Report|language=en|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015204855/http://www.the-businessreport.com/article/swee-bridges-brunei-together/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xe.com/currencyconverter/convert/?Amount=138900000&From=BND&To=USD|title=XE: Convert BND/USD. Brunei Darussalam Dollar to United States Dollar|website=XE Money Transfer|language=en|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2018-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108062637/http://www.xe.com/currencyconverter/convert/?Amount=138900000&From=BND&To=USD|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原计划2016年6月25日建成，但由于甘榜宾都马林（Kampung Pintu Malim）拆迁地区的一些居民仍未迁出，以及其他技术原因，启用日期被迫推迟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.seehua.com/?p=185163|title=双溪哥本桥延至明年完工|date=2016-07-04|publisher=诗华日报|access-date=2018-01-07|archive-date=2019-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916174548/http://news.seehua.com/?p=185163|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bt.com.bn/frontpage-news-national/2016/07/04/snag-hits-sg-kebun-bridge-opening#sthash.m7HL3dje.igcG5L8j.dpbs|title=Snag hits Sg Kebun bridge opening|author=Wail Wardi Wasil|date=2016-07-04|publisher=The Brunei Times|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710132340/http://bt.com.bn/frontpage-news-national/2016/07/04/snag-hits-sg-kebun-bridge-opening#sthash.m7HL3dje.igcG5L8j.dpbs|archivedate=2016-07-10|accessdate=2016-07-09}}</ref>。

大桥于2017年10月2日起开始试运行<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://borneobulletin.com.bn/trial-opening-of-new-sungai-kebun-bridge/|title=Trial opening of new Sungai Kebun Bridge|date=2017-10-01|work=Borneo Bulletin Online|language=en|access-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015205140/https://borneobulletin.com.bn/trial-opening-of-new-sungai-kebun-bridge/|archive-date=2017-10-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":4" />。10月14日，双溪哥本大桥启用仪式在庆祝文莱苏丹[[登基|登基]]五十周年大型音乐[[焰火|焰火]]晚会上隆重举行，焰火展示由霍华德、湖南浏阳梦想烟花和银达利焰火公司联合燃放，同时还进行了[[花车巡游|花车巡游]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.brudirect.com/news.php?id=34811|title=Opening of Sungai Kebun Bridge, the Decorated Floats and Boats Procession and Fireworks Display|website=Brunei's No.1 News Website|language=en|accessdate=2018-01-07|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015205050/https://www.brudirect.com/news.php?id=34811|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://borneobulletin.com.bn/pyrotechnic-marvel-to-illuminate-bridge-launch/|title=Pyrotechnic marvel to illuminate bridge launch|date=2017-10-14|work=Borneo Bulletin Online|language=en|access-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015184804/http://borneobulletin.com.bn/pyrotechnic-marvel-to-illuminate-bridge-launch/|archive-date=2017-10-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ofireworks.com/news/shownews.php?lang=cn&id=40|title=花开“一带一路”：浏阳焰火绽放文莱 助阵苏丹登基50周年庆典|date=2017-10-17|publisher=烟花玩家|access-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108062733/http://www.ofireworks.com/news/shownews.php?lang=cn&id=40|archive-date=2018-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

